\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces E3: depth-$L$ $1$-WL refinement funnels on Cora (left) and ogbn-arxiv (right). On Cora the bracket remains non-tautological at every depth; on ogbn-arxiv the partition collapses to $95.6\%$ singleton cells by $L = 3$ and both bracket endpoints pinch to $0$, the asymptotic predicted by \cref  {prop:refine-discrete}. Four more datasets in \texttt  {experiments/figures/}.}}{20}{figure.3}\protected@file@percent }
